snippet.title: O Morning Star | Kyle Pederson
snippet.description:
O Morning Star is an iconic hymn reimagined here by Kyle Pederson. It is scored for unaccompanied SATB choir with divisi. 

The timeless message is reharmonized and adapted for a contemporary audience. This hymn and its setting will be a good fit for capable church choirs along with community and collegiate-level ensembles.

Performance by Transept, conducted by Timothy J. Campbell.

Video production by Brian Gaukel. 

Purchase the music: https://giamusic.com/resource/o-morning-star-printed-music-ww2079
